                    <span>Having seen Michael Wilkinson in action, I can assure you that his secrets are the best!  I attended a facilitation training session by his company when I worked for Coca-Cola - and now everyone can learn those same tips and guidelines...plus a whole lot more.  Would recommend it to new and seasoned faciliators - there is something for everyone.  Enjoy!</span>
                  
              
